{
  "texts": [
    "This error is common on the long-form QA datasetsfoot_2 ASQA and ELI5, and it directly impacts Citation Precision.",
    "Misinterpretation of cited passages (63.16%).We notice that our LLMs's responses are more extractive after training.",
    "However, the model may still interpret and paraphrase the facts mentioned in the passages incorrectly.",
    "There are two subcategories.",
    "The first is misinterpretation of a single passage (52.63%), where facts in a single passage are distorted."
  ]
}